attributes.body: Product description Kush Mints is a hybrid weed strain made from a genetic cross between Animal Mints and Bubba Kush. This strain is 50% sativa and 50% indica. It has a balanced high that is both relaxing and euphoric, with a pleasant body buzz and a creative mind. About this strain: Kush Mints Info Kush Mints is a cross of Bubba Kush pollen and the clone-only Animal Mints strain bred by Seed Junky Genetics in Southern California. attributes.body: Craft Cannabis Massage Oil 100mg THC/ 100mg CBD, 1oz compostable wheat straw bottle Perfect for promoting full body relaxation and comfort, with a calming and peaceful Lavender scent Time & Care In Each Batch Our salves are artisanally made with the time and care a sacred medicine deserves. Each small batch is meticulously made by hand and takes over 48 hours to craft, resulting in a smooth, emollient that provides ultimate relief. Most salves use an alcohol stripping method, where the cannabis trichomes are ripped away from the plant, or it is made by hastily throwing in all parts of the plant in oil to generate quick, large yields. This makes for a green, very pungent oil that has a greasy and petroleum-type feel. At NM Sacred Flower, our artisans take the time and extra step to use a gentle, chemical-free extraction method inspired by respect and love of the healing plant. Our unique infusion process takes over 8 hours, which ensures a soft, creamy and therapeutic salve that is soothingly aromatic. Our careful technique has taken over five years to master, bringing you holistic healing of the finest quality. This spirit and journey of our New Mexican craft is hand packaged and delivered to you. May our salve bring you relief, peace and healing.
